As his fighter streaked through the skies of europe, central america and 
asia, Daemos' board computer told him that the signature of Tarantulas had 
disappeared. He sighed.

Daemos:
Computer, locate probable predacon base location. I need to find Tarantulas 
at all costs!

But his passage was not a discreet one. Anyone who had functionning sensors 
and optics could easily notice him flying by.
